            . I lost two sides of bacon and a sack. I met the prisoner between three and four o'clock at Shepherd's Bush; he got out of my waggon between <placeName id="t17730707-11-crimeloc66">Colnbrook</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17730707-11-crimeloc66" type="placeName" value="Colnbrook"></interp>
