             I am a peace officer; I was sent for to the Plough; I found the prisoner with a sack and the bacon. (The bacon and the sack produced).</p>
               <p>Prosecutor. That is the sack; there is the name of 
               <persName id="t17730707-11-person202">
                  Edward
                   Bartholomew
               <interp inst="t17730707-11-person202" type="surname" value="Bartholomew"></interp>
